data.description: Located in highly desirable Riverwood Subdivision.  Open floor plan with large windows overlooking backyard oasis and swimming pool.  Kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and undercabinet lighting.  Home includes private mother-in-law suite or game room that includes second kitchen area with dishwasher, stove, and sink.  Mother-in-law suite can be accessed through private entrance.  New AC unit March 2022.
